{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "蒸汽升騰", "storyInfo": "城防軍總指揮官萊托中校來到工廠主持了換旗儀式。半路上的費斯特與工廠裡的凱瑟琳共同見證了這一幕。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數天後"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_053", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_053", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如何？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_053", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清點完了，這一批的工廠都上交了指定數量的資材。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_053", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳女士，你知道的，接收倫蒂尼姆數百家工廠，還要保證它們順利運轉並不是一件輕鬆的事。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為此，我不得不親自完成每一場交接。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其中總是會有一些不愉快的事，而這一次的交接，在最後一批工廠中，是最順利的。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你願意配合，為我節省了許多時間，我必須感謝你。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不想做一些徒勞無功的事罷了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我欣賞你的態度，凱瑟琳女士。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我恐怕，你內心深處並不是這麼想的。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，貴工廠前幾天，有工人跑了，所以，我想順便清點一下人數，看一看貴工廠的名冊。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......跑掉的那個，是我的孫子。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕人，總是很急躁。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很坦誠，凱瑟琳女士，但這並不是坦誠就能解決的事。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，我不能保證手下的所有人都一條心，我沒有那個本事。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能保證工廠交上指定數額的資材。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以理解為，你希望我放過他嗎？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個毛都沒長齊的小鬼，並不能影響工廠運轉。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你可以。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說過你的事蹟，凱瑟琳女士。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不愧是曾被選為工人代表的女傑，令人敬佩。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們總要撲滅這樣的苗頭，還是說，你可以保證，你的孫子不會成為反抗我們的一員，比如......加入最近興起的自救軍。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不需要保證，長官。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕人總是以為自己能做到些什麼。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們往往不知道自己面對的是什麼。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們......會自取滅亡的。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我明白你的意思了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誠然，追究一個工人的逃脫，遠比不上維持十幾座工廠的穩定運轉來得重要。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以忘記這件事，凱瑟琳女士。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我希望你也能信守你的承諾。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我負責的工廠，永遠不會出問題。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好，那麼，該去進行交接儀式了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053", "name2": "avg_npc_054", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真倒楣，我也想去工廠那邊看升旗。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053", "name2": "avg_npc_054", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別抱怨了，這裡也看得到旗杆，你就湊合一下吧。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053", "name2": "avg_npc_054", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡看，哪有在現場看有意義。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖，真沒想到，我們居然真的拿下了維多利亞的首都，放以前，真是做夢都不敢想啊。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053", "name2": "avg_npc_054", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......確實。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，接下來才是最困難的時候，大公爵都在盯著我們。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053", "name2": "avg_npc_054", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，如果他們有用，我們也不會這麼輕鬆地奪下倫蒂尼姆了。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053", "name2": "avg_npc_054"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好險......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，幸好這些雇傭兵根本不知道從這裡可以進入地塊縫隙。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特走到了一個管道入口前。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他調查過，這條管道的某處，可以通往薩迪恩區。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是當他真的要踏入這個管道時，他終究還是猶豫了。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他沒有騙帕特，他是把自己會遇到的困難都想了個遍。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可他沒有說出來的是，他並沒有所有問題的解決方案。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟奶奶說得沒錯，他只是個工匠，有一個還算聰明的腦袋，和相當勤勞的雙手。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩樣東西能確保他在和平年代的倫蒂尼姆混個好日子，卻不一定能讓他在薩卡茲的眼皮子底下保住性命。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "湯米說得對，要是那些又高又大的鐵傢伙還在就好了。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他長這麼大了，都還沒見過蒸汽騎士呢。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g4_ordnancefactory", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metalpipe", "volume": 0.5, "loop": "true", "channel": "pipe"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噹啷。噹啷。噹啷。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工廠的天花板很高，天窗不大，從裡面能看見的天空總是很小。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變幻的天色在工廠內部留下相似的投影，同樣不變的還有流水線上一塊金屬敲擊著另一塊金屬的聲響——"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及總是站在流水線旁的奶奶的背影。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "pipe", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是覺得很枯燥？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "握緊你的錘子和扳手。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真想做出點什麼來，你就得堅持住。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你敲一下，你只會收獲一塊爛鐵塊。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你敲了一下又一下，你能造出蒸汽甲胄。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你敲了一下又一下，然後你的孩子，孩子們的孩子接著敲——", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們就有了倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他該回去嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他該前進嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他不知道。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_horn", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天邊響起了屬於薩卡茲的號角聲，費斯特循聲望去。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一座倫蒂尼姆工廠的頂上，都豎立著一面旗幟。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是代表著維多利亞的旗幟。"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自工廠建成以來，這一點從未有過改變。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這一點，將在今天被改變。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡簽字吧，凱瑟琳女士。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳沒有猶豫，在代表著工廠權力轉移的文件上，簽下了練習過的簽名。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，就是最後的換旗了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留下吧，凱瑟琳女士。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，你正在見證歷史。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，我可以抽煙嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請便。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_lighter", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smokefemale", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，就像你聽說過我一樣，我也聽說過一些你的事情。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高盧。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是的，家父是高盧遺民，這並不是一個秘密。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你是在問我此時此刻的感受，凱瑟琳女士。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我因這個過程中沒有流血而感到一瞬間的喜悅，但除此之外，我的心中只有悲傷。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_flag", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處，薩卡茲戰士們搬來了屬於他們的旗幟。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外兩個薩卡茲戰士則做好了降旗的準備。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳能看到他們臉上的喜色。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越過他們，則是絢麗的晚霞。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳知道，這意味著，黑暗已經不遠了。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特回頭看去，從這個位置，他正好能夠看到工廠高聳的旗杆。"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他就這麼站在那裡，看著屬於維多利亞的旗幟緩緩降下。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "片刻之後，屬於薩卡茲的旗幟被緩緩升起。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿一切都沒有改變。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他深深吸了一口氣，跳入管道。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管道中一片黑暗，他帶著忐忑，向記憶中的薩迪恩區方向，開始前進。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一天，倫蒂尼姆所有軍工廠完成了交接，並且換上了屬於薩卡茲的旗幟。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們迎風飄揚。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}